<span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> getNextActiveElement = <span class="hljs-function">(<span class="hljs-params">list, activeElement, shouldGetNext, isCycleAllowed</span>) =&gt;</span> {
  <span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> index = list.indexOf(activeElement); <span class="hljs-comment">// if the element does not exist in the list return an element depending on the direction and if cycle is allowed</span>

  <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (index === <span class="hljs-number">-1</span>) {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> list[!shouldGetNext &amp;&amp; isCycleAllowed ? list.length - <span class="hljs-number">1</span> : <span class="hljs-number">0</span>];
  }

  <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> listLength = list.length;
  index += shouldGetNext ? <span class="hljs-number">1</span> : <span class="hljs-number">-1</span>;

  <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (isCycleAllowed) {
    index = (index + listLength) % listLength;
  }

  <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> list[<span class="hljs-built_in">Math</span>.max(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-built_in">Math</span>.min(index, listLength - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>))];
};

<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title">removeHandler</span>(<span class="hljs-params">element, events, typeEvent, handler, delegationSelector</span>) </span>{
  <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> fn = findHandler(events[typeEvent], handler, delegationSelector);

  <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!fn) {

  <span class="hljs-keyword">delete</span> events[typeEvent][fn.uidEvent];

<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title">removeNamespacedHandlers</span>(<span class="hljs-params">element, events, typeEvent, namespace</span>) </span>{
  <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> storeElementEvent = events[typeEvent] || {};

    }
  });

<span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> SelectorEngine = {
  find(selector, element = <span class="hljs-built_in">document</span>.documentElement) {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> [].concat(...Element.prototype.querySelectorAll.call(element, selector));
  },

  findOne(selector, element = <span class="hljs-built_in">document</span>.documentElement) {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> Element.prototype.querySelector.call(element, selector);
  },

  children(element, selector) {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> [].concat(...element.children).filter(<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-params">child</span> =&gt;</span> child.matches(selector));
  },

  parents(element, selector) {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> parents = [];
    <span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> ancestor = element.parentNode;

    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (ancestor &amp;&amp; ancestor.nodeType === Node.ELEMENT_NODE &amp;&amp; ancestor.nodeType !== NODE_TEXT) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (ancestor.matches(selector)) {
        parents.push(ancestor);
      }

      ancestor = ancestor.parentNode;
    }

    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> parents;
  },

  prev(element, selector) {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> previous = element.previousElementSibling;

    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (previous) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (previous.matches(selector)) {
        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> [previous];
      }

      previous = previous.previousElementSibling;
    }

    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> [];
  },

  next(element, selector) {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> next = element.nextElementSibling;

    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (next) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (next.matches(selector)) {
        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> [next];
      }

      next = next.nextElementSibling;
    }

    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> [];
  },

  focusableChildren(element) {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> focusables = [<span class="hljs-string">'a'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'button'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'input'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'textarea'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'select'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'details'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'[tabindex]'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'[contenteditable="true"]'</span>].map(<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-params">selector</span> =&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-string">`<span class="hljs-subst">${selector}</span>:not([tabindex^="-"])`</span>).join(<span class="hljs-string">', '</span>);
    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.find(focusables, element).filter(<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-params">el</span> =&gt;</span> !isDisabled(el) &amp;&amp; isVisible(el));

    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> target = getElementFromSelector(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>);

    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!target || !target.classList.contains(CLASS_NAME_CAROUSEL)) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;
    }

    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> config = { ...Manipulator.getDataAttributes(target),
      ...Manipulator.getDataAttributes(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>)
    };
    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> slideIndex = <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.getAttribute(<span class="hljs-string">'data-bs-slide-to'</span>);

    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (slideIndex) {
      config.interval = <span class="hljs-literal">false</span>;
    }

    Carousel.carouselInterface(target, config);

    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (slideIndex) {
      Carousel.getInstance(target).to(slideIndex);
    }

    event.preventDefault();
  }

}

<span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">FocusTrap</span> </span>{
  <span class="hljs-keyword">constructor</span>(config) {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._config = <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._getConfig(config);
    <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._isActive = <span class="hljs-literal">false</span>;
    <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._lastTabNavDirection = <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>;
  }

  activate() {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> {
      trapElement,
      autofocus
    } = <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._config;

    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._isActive) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;
    }

    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (autofocus) {
      trapElement.focus();
    }

    EventHandler.off(<span class="hljs-built_in">document</span>, EVENT_KEY$<span class="hljs-number">7</span>); <span class="hljs-comment">// guard against infinite focus loop</span>

    EventHandler.on(<span class="hljs-built_in">document</span>, EVENT_FOCUSIN$<span class="hljs-number">1</span>, event =&gt; <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._handleFocusin(event));
    EventHandler.on(<span class="hljs-built_in">document</span>, EVENT_KEYDOWN_TAB, event =&gt; <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._handleKeydown(event));
    <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._isActive = <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>;
  }

  deactivate() {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._isActive) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;
    }

    <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._isActive = <span class="hljs-literal">false</span>;
    EventHandler.off(<span class="hljs-built_in">document</span>, EVENT_KEY$<span class="hljs-number">7</span>);
  } <span class="hljs-comment">// Private</span>


  _handleFocusin(event) {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> {
      target
    } = event;
    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> {
      trapElement
    } = <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._config;

    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (target === <span class="hljs-built_in">document</span> || target === trapElement || trapElement.contains(target)) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;
    }

    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> elements = SelectorEngine.focusableChildren(trapElement);

    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (elements.length === <span class="hljs-number">0</span>) {
      trapElement.focus();
    } <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._lastTabNavDirection === TAB_NAV_BACKWARD) {
      elements[elements.length - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>].focus();
    } <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> {
      elements[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>].focus();
    }
  }

  _handleKeydown(event) {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (event.key !== TAB_KEY) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;
    }

    <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._lastTabNavDirection = event.shiftKey ? TAB_NAV_BACKWARD : TAB_NAV_FORWARD;
  }

  _getConfig(config) {
    config = { ...Default$<span class="hljs-number">6</span>,
      ...(<span class="hljs-keyword">typeof</span> config === <span class="hljs-string">'object'</span> ? config : {})
    };
    typeCheckConfig(NAME$<span class="hljs-number">7</span>, config, DefaultType$<span class="hljs-number">6</span>);
    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> config;
  }

        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;
      }

      <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._enter(<span class="hljs-literal">null</span>, <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>);
    }
  }

  _setListeners() {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> triggers = <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._config.trigger.split(<span class="hljs-string">' '</span>);

    triggers.forEach(<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-params">trigger</span> =&gt;</span> {

        <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> eventIn = trigger === TRIGGER_HOVER ? <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.constructor.Event.MOUSEENTER : <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.constructor.Event.FOCUSIN;
        <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> eventOut = trigger === TRIGGER_HOVER ? <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.constructor.Event.MOUSELEAVE : <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.constructor.Event.FOCUSOUT;
        EventHandler.on(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element, eventIn, <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._config.selector, event =&gt; <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._enter(event));
        EventHandler.on(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element, eventOut, <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._config.selector, event =&gt; <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._leave(event));
      }
    });

    <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._hideModalHandler = <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-params">()</span> =&gt;</span> {

      <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._config = { ...this._config,
        <span class="hljs-attr">trigger</span>: <span class="hljs-string">'manual'</span>,
        <span class="hljs-attr">selector</span>: <span class="hljs-string">''</span>

      <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._fixTitle();

  _fixTitle() {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> title = <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.getAttribute(<span class="hljs-string">'title'</span>);

    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> originalTitleType = <span class="hljs-keyword">typeof</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.getAttribute(<span class="hljs-string">'data-bs-original-title'</span>);

    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (title || originalTitleType !== <span class="hljs-string">'string'</span>) {

      <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (title &amp;&amp; !<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.getAttribute(<span class="hljs-string">'aria-label'</span>) &amp;&amp; !<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.textContent) {
        <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.setAttribute(<span class="hljs-string">'aria-label'</span>, title);
      }

      <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.setAttribute(<span class="hljs-string">'title'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">''</span>);
    }
  }

  _enter(event, context) {
    context = <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._initializeOnDelegatedTarget(event, context);

    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (event) {
      context._activeTrigger[event.type === <span class="hljs-string">'focusin'</span> ? TRIGGER_FOCUS : TRIGGER_HOVER] = <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>;
    }

    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (context.getTipElement().classList.contains(CLASS_NAME_SHOW$<span class="hljs-number">2</span>) || context._hoverState === HOVER_STATE_SHOW) {
      context._hoverState = HOVER_STATE_SHOW;
      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;
    }

    clearTimeout(context._timeout);
    context._hoverState = HOVER_STATE_SHOW;

    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!context._config.delay || !context._config.delay.show) {
      context.show();
      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;
    }

    context._timeout = setTimeout(<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-params">()</span> =&gt;</span> {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (context._hoverState === HOVER_STATE_SHOW) {
        context.show();
      }
    }, context._config.delay.show);
  }

  _leave(event, context) {
    context = <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._initializeOnDelegatedTarget(event, context);

    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (event) {
      context._activeTrigger[event.type === <span class="hljs-string">'focusout'</span> ? TRIGGER_FOCUS : TRIGGER_HOVER] = context._element.contains(event.relatedTarget);
    }

    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (context._isWithActiveTrigger()) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;
    }

    clearTimeout(context._timeout);
    context._hoverState = HOVER_STATE_OUT;

    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!context._config.delay || !context._config.delay.hide) {
      context.hide();

EventHandler.on(<span class="hljs-built_in">document</span>, EVENT_CLICK_DATA_API, SELECTOR_DATA_TOGGLE, <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> (<span class="hljs-params">event</span>) </span>{

<span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> NAME = <span class="hljs-string">'toast'</span>;
<span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> DATA_KEY = <span class="hljs-string">'bs.toast'</span>;

<span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> EVENT_MOUSEOUT = <span class="hljs-string">`mouseout<span class="hljs-subst">${EVENT_KEY}</span>`</span>;

<span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> EVENT_FOCUSOUT = <span class="hljs-string">`focusout<span class="hljs-subst">${EVENT_KEY}</span>`</span>;
<span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> EVENT_HIDE = <span class="hljs-string">`hide<span class="hljs-subst">${EVENT_KEY}</span>`</span>;
<span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> EVENT_HIDDEN = <span class="hljs-string">`hidden<span class="hljs-subst">${EVENT_KEY}</span>`</span>;

<span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> EVENT_SHOWN = <span class="hljs-string">`shown<span class="hljs-subst">${EVENT_KEY}</span>`</span>;
<span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> CLASS_NAME_FADE = <span class="hljs-string">'fade'</span>;
<span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> CLASS_NAME_HIDE = <span class="hljs-string">'hide'</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">// @deprecated - kept here only for backwards compatibility</span>

<span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> CLASS_NAME_SHOW = <span class="hljs-string">'show'</span>;
<span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> CLASS_NAME_SHOWING = <span class="hljs-string">'showing'</span>;
<span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> DefaultType = {
  <span class="hljs-attr">animation</span>: <span class="hljs-string">'boolean'</span>,

  <span class="hljs-attr">autohide</span>: <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>,

<span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">Toast</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">extends</span> <span class="hljs-title">BaseComponent</span> </span>{
  <span class="hljs-keyword">constructor</span>(element, config) {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">super</span>(element);
    <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._config = <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._getConfig(config);
    <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._timeout = <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>;
    <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._hasMouseInteraction = <span class="hljs-literal">false</span>;
    <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._hasKeyboardInteraction = <span class="hljs-literal">false</span>;

    <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._setListeners();
  } <span class="hljs-comment">// Getters</span>


  <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">get</span> DefaultType() {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> DefaultType;
  }

  <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">get</span> Default() {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> Default;
  }

  <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">get</span> NAME() {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> NAME;
  } <span class="hljs-comment">// Public</span>


  show() {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> showEvent = EventHandler.trigger(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element, EVENT_SHOW);

    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (showEvent.defaultPrevented) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;
    }

    <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._clearTimeout();

    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._config.animation) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.classList.add(CLASS_NAME_FADE);
    }

    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> complete = <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-params">()</span> =&gt;</span> {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.classList.remove(CLASS_NAME_SHOWING);

      EventHandler.trigger(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element, EVENT_SHOWN);

      <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._maybeScheduleHide();
    };

    <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.classList.remove(CLASS_NAME_HIDE); <span class="hljs-comment">// @deprecated</span>


    reflow(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element);

    <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.classList.add(CLASS_NAME_SHOW);

    <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.classList.add(CLASS_NAME_SHOWING);

    <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._queueCallback(complete, <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element, <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._config.animation);
  }

  hide() {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.classList.contains(CLASS_NAME_SHOW)) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;
    }

    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> hideEvent = EventHandler.trigger(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element, EVENT_HIDE);

    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (hideEvent.defaultPrevented) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;
    }

    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> complete = <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-params">()</span> =&gt;</span> {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.classList.add(CLASS_NAME_HIDE); <span class="hljs-comment">// @deprecated</span>


      <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.classList.remove(CLASS_NAME_SHOWING);

      <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.classList.remove(CLASS_NAME_SHOW);

      EventHandler.trigger(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element, EVENT_HIDDEN);
    };

    <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.classList.add(CLASS_NAME_SHOWING);

    <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._queueCallback(complete, <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element, <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._config.animation);
  }

  dispose() {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._clearTimeout();

    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.classList.contains(CLASS_NAME_SHOW)) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.classList.remove(CLASS_NAME_SHOW);
    }

    <span class="hljs-keyword">super</span>.dispose();
  } <span class="hljs-comment">// Private</span>


  _getConfig(config) {
    config = { ...Default,
      ...Manipulator.getDataAttributes(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element),
      ...(<span class="hljs-keyword">typeof</span> config === <span class="hljs-string">'object'</span> &amp;&amp; config ? config : {})
    };
    typeCheckConfig(NAME, config, <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.constructor.DefaultType);
    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> config;
  }

  _maybeScheduleHide() {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._config.autohide) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;
    }

    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._hasMouseInteraction || <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._hasKeyboardInteraction) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;
    }

    <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._timeout = setTimeout(<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-params">()</span> =&gt;</span> {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.hide();
    }, <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._config.delay);
  }

  _onInteraction(event, isInteracting) {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">switch</span> (event.type) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> <span class="hljs-string">'mouseover'</span>:
      <span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> <span class="hljs-string">'mouseout'</span>:
        <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._hasMouseInteraction = isInteracting;
        <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;

      <span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> <span class="hljs-string">'focusin'</span>:
      <span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> <span class="hljs-string">'focusout'</span>:
        <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._hasKeyboardInteraction = isInteracting;
        <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;
    }

    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (isInteracting) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._clearTimeout();

      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;
    }

    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> nextElement = event.relatedTarget;

    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element === nextElement || <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.contains(nextElement)) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;
    }

    <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._maybeScheduleHide();
  }

  _setListeners() {
    EventHandler.on(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element, EVENT_MOUSEOVER, event =&gt; <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._onInteraction(event, <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>));
    EventHandler.on(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element, EVENT_MOUSEOUT, event =&gt; <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._onInteraction(event, <span class="hljs-literal">false</span>));
    EventHandler.on(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element, EVENT_FOCUSIN, event =&gt; <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._onInteraction(event, <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>));
    EventHandler.on(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element, EVENT_FOCUSOUT, event =&gt; <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._onInteraction(event, <span class="hljs-literal">false</span>));
  }

  _clearTimeout() {
    clearTimeout(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._timeout);
    <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._timeout = <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>;
  } <span class="hljs-comment">// Static</span>


  <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> jQueryInterface(config) {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.each(<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> (<span class="hljs-params"></span>) </span>{
      <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> data = Toast.getOrCreateInstance(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>, config);

      <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">typeof</span> config === <span class="hljs-string">'string'</span>) {
        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">typeof</span> data[config] === <span class="hljs-string">'undefined'</span>) {
          <span class="hljs-keyword">throw</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">TypeError</span>(<span class="hljs-string">`No method named "<span class="hljs-subst">${config}</span>"`</span>);
        }

        data[config](<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>);
      }
    });
  }

}

enableDismissTrigger(Toast);
